node.text:
•

F.E.A.R= Finally, Exiting, Average, Reality
•

In order for us to tap into that next orbit of our lives, we have to leave the fear behind.
•

Fear keeps us average, and i’ll be honest.. You are Extrodinary in so many aspects of your life.
•

But you’ll never tap in because you’re choosing F.E.A.R
•

You’ve become accustomed to not living on your higher self.
•

If a eagle lived with chickens, he’d accept the fact that he couldn’t soar.
•

It’s time for you to soar, it’s time for you to over come F.E.A.R.
•

It’s Time for you to live the life you Want.
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW

node.title: I Will No Longer Fertilize My Fears

node.text:
Robin Hood IPO’d yesterday & theres a lot of concern for what it can do whether to invest in it or not.
•

I just dropped a YouTube video from my live yesterday on my thoughts on the Robinhood IPO
•

While im not a fan of the app itself, I do realize the company is extremely young & does have a bright Future.
•

Most young investors will gravitate to Robinhood because it’s more user friendly compared to the bigger companies.
•

And with the stock market becoming more and more popular that along will give the company good growth projections.
•

Will they be profitable that’s a story that still has to be unfolded.
•

We do know that Cathy Woods made an investment in the company, but that doesn’t mean you should or shouldn’t.
•

All investments should be based on your ability to research them and find value.
•
